{"claim_type": "technical-statement", "line_end": 336, "line_start": 336, "page_hint": null, "section": "Ornl Dwg. 69-10965", "text": "Studies on the validity of the asymptotic approach premise were motivated by Seldin's<sup>4</sup> demonstrations that test specimens can be made to reproduce their original stress-strain responses in the longitudinal and lateral directions by heat treating them at their graphitization temperatures."}
