{"claim_type": "figure-reference", "line_end": 371, "line_start": 371, "page_hint": null, "section": "Ornl Dwg. 69-2975", "text": "Figures 19 and 20 show that the history was almost entirely removed by heat treatment."}
{"claim_type": "measurement", "line_end": 419, "line_start": 419, "page_hint": null, "section": "Ornl Dwg. 69-2972", "text": "In addition to the investigations just described, studies were made to examine the influence of hold time at $3000^{\\circ}\\mathrm{C}$ ."}
